						<summary>

						<p>On a slab on the brink of a well near the Siddhēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>1184 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Krōdhi, Vaisākha śu. 8, Thursday. The palaeography of the epigraph being of about the 12th century, the date may be equated to 1184 A.D., April 19, Thursday, f.d.t. °07.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of Chindiya Chandaṇṇa of Muḷugunda in a fight.</p>						

						</summary>
